insert into `odd_ingredients` values (4685,'Bot','2 oz Cranberry juice \r\n2 oz Vodka (Skyy) \r\n1/2 oz Triple sec \r\n1/2 oz Lime juice \r\n1 dash Orange juice','The easy way to make this drink is to add all listed ingredients with ice into shaker and strain into glass. However, the really slick way is much more impressive: Add cranberry juice, lime juice, tripple sec and only one ounce vodka into shaker with ice. Strain into glass. Then, mix 1 once orange juice with one ounce vodka in a seperate glass. Fill a turkey baister with the vodka/OJ mix, and slowly inject it into the cranberry glass on the bottom. This produces a sort of reverse-layering effect, and also ensures both cranberry and OJ will have the same amount of vodka.','Ordinary Drink','Highball glass','Alcoholic','Cranberry juice,Vodka,Triple sec,Lime juice,Orange juice');
